      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUMBLE SMILES (8) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Whistle Wave (19.53) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Makes plenty of appeal. CANYA SUPERSONIC (5) has not raced since scoring (20.24) over 350m at Goulburn ten weeks ago. Has a good record here including two wins. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. MAGIC LINKIN (1) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 4.5 lengths (19.32). Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Better than last start and can bounce back. TOWERING LUKE (4) is always a threat when he races at this journey.",
